name: are-scripts-enabled
description: Dependency to test whether yarn scripts are enabled.
author: alxndrsn <alxndrsn>

scripts.preinstall: echo '!!! UNEXPECTED SCRIPT RUN: preinstall ' && false
scripts.install: echo '!!! UNEXPECTED SCRIPT RUN: install    ' && false
scripts.postinstall: echo '!!! UNEXPECTED SCRIPT RUN: postinstall' && false
